## 5. What did NOT cause empty-shell corruption

| Action | Verdict |
|--------|---------|
| `flask migrate-db` (additive) | Does **not** DELETE rows; only ALTER + create_all |
| Template / HTML / JS changes | No DB access |
| `calibration_utils.py` display logic | Read-only at runtime |
| AstroBin export modal UI | No schema writes |
| Auto-restore (when it existed briefly) | Could overwrite with wrong backup; removed entirely — not the drop-table mechanism |

