## 13. Quick checklist before any DB-touching agent task

- [ ] Is Flask dev server stopped? (If not, ask user.)
- [ ] Is this task UI-only? (If yes, do not touch DB.)
- [ ] Am I importing `app` from a script? (Use sqlite3 instead.)
- [ ] Am I running anything with `drop_all` / `DROP TABLE`? (Stop; use temp DB.)
- [ ] Did I run `diagnose_db.py` before and after?
